high_descs: Walk towards the wall, then hang a left and walk over to the end of the kitchen island.
Pick up the leftmost closest butter knife off of the kitchen island.
Turn right and walk over to the oven.
Put the knife in the glass that is on the counter to the left of the oven.
Pick up the glass with the butter knife in it off of the counter.
Walk back over to the kitchen island.
Put the glass with the butter knife in it on the island.
anns.task_desc: Put a glass with a butter knife in it on the kitchen island.

high_descs: Turn left and walk to the table to your left.
Grab the knife sitting on the table.
Turn right and walk to the stove to your right.
Place the knife in the glass cup on the counter to the left of the stove.
Pick up the glass cup on the counter with the knife in it.
Turn around and take the glass cup with the knife in it to the table to your left.
Place the glass cup with the knife in it on the counter between the black cup and knife.
anns.task_desc: Place a glass cup with knife it on the table.

high_descs: Turn around and step to the right to face the end of the center table.
Pick up the knife on the center table.
Turn right and walk across the room and turn right to face the counter.
Put the knife in the cup on the counter.
Pick up the cup with a knife in it on the counter.
Turn right and walk forward to face the center table.
Place the glass with a knife in it on the center table in the kitchen.
anns.task_desc: To put a knife in a glass and place them on the center table.
